main event: A report was filed regarding a UFO sighting in Lyndhurst, Ohio, on February 13, 1968.
interesting points: The observer expressed certainty that the object was not a conventional aircraft., The report lacks specific details about the number of objects and their observation length., No photographs were provided with the report., The Air Force requested further information from the observer via an attached form., The conclusion stated there was insufficient data for evaluation.
witness description: an individual who reported seeing an unidentified object
